{"data":[{"name":"78:1","price":"Sur quoi s’interrogent-ils mutuellement ?","arabic":"عَمَّ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5673,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:2","price":"Sur la grande nouvelle,","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلنَّبَإِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5674,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:3","price":"à propos de laquelle ils divergent.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي هُمۡ فِيهِ مُخۡتَلِفُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5675,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:4","price":"Eh bien non! Ils sauront bientôt.","arabic":"كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5676,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:5","price":"Encore une fois, non! Ils sauront bientôt.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5677,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:6","price":"N’avons-Nous pas fait de la terre une couche ?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ مِهَٰدٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5678,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:7","price":"et (placé) les montagnes comme des piquets ?","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَوۡتَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5679,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:8","price":"Nous vous avons créés en couples,","arabic":"وَخَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5680,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:9","price":"et désigné votre sommeil pour votre repos,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا نَوۡمَكُمۡ سُبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5681,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:10","price":"et fait de la nuit un vêtement,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلَّيۡلَ لِبَاسٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5682,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:11","price":"et assigné le jour pour les affaires de la vie,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلنَّهَارَ مَعَاشٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5683,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:12","price":"et construit au-dessus de vous sept (cieux) renforcés,","arabic":"وَبَنَيۡنَا فَوۡقَكُمۡ سَبۡعٗا شِدَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5684,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:13","price":"et [y] avons placé une lampe (le soleil) très ardente,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا سِرَاجٗا وَهَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5685,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:14","price":"et fait descendre des nuées une eau abondante.","arabic":"وَأَنزَلۡنَا مِنَ ٱلۡمُعۡصِرَٰتِ مَآءٗ ثَجَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5686,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:15","price":"pour faire pousser par elle grains et plantes.","arabic":"لِّنُخۡرِجَ بِهِۦ حَبّٗا وَنَبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5687,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:16","price":"et jardins luxuriants.","arabic":"وَجَنَّٰتٍ أَلۡفَافًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5688,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:17","price":"Le Jour de la Décision [du Jugement] a son terme fixé.","arabic":"إِنَّ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ كَانَ مِيقَٰتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5689,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:18","price":"Le jour où l’on soufflera dans la Trompe, vous viendrez par troupes,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يُنفَخُ فِي ٱلصُّورِ فَتَأۡتُونَ أَفۡوَاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5690,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:19","price":"et le ciel sera ouvert et [présentera] des portes,","arabic":"وَفُتِحَتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتۡ أَبۡوَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5691,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:20","price":"et les montagnes seront mises en marche et deviendront un mirage.","arabic":"وَسُيِّرَتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ فَكَانَتۡ سَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5692,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:21","price":"L’Enfer demeure aux aguets.","arabic":"إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتۡ مِرۡصَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5693,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:22","price":"refuge pour les transgresseurs.","arabic":"لِّلطَّٰغِينَ مَـَٔابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5694,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:23","price":"Ils y demeureront pendant des siècles successifs.","arabic":"لَّٰبِثِينَ فِيهَآ أَحۡقَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5695,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:24","price":"Ils n’y goûteront ni fraîcheur ni breuvage,","arabic":"لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرۡدٗا وَلَا شَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5696,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:25","price":"Hormis une eau bouillante et un pus.","arabic":"إِلَّا حَمِيمٗا وَغَسَّاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5697,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:26","price":"comme rétribution équitable.","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ وِفَاقًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5698,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:27","price":"Car ils ne s’attendaient pas à rendre compte,","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ لَا يَرۡجُونَ حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5699,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:28","price":"et traitaient de mensonges, continuellement, Nos versets.","arabic":"وَكَذَّبُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا كِذَّابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5700,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:29","price":"alors que Nous avons dénombré toutes choses en écrit.","arabic":"وَكُلَّ شَيۡءٍ أَحۡصَيۡنَٰهُ كِتَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5701,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:30","price":"Goûtez-donc. Nous n’augmenterons pour vous que le châtiment !","arabic":"فَذُوقُواْ فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمۡ إِلَّا عَذَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5702,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:31","price":"Pour les pieux ce sera une réussite :","arabic":"إِنَّ لِلۡمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5703,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:32","price":"jardins et vignes,","arabic":"حَدَآئِقَ وَأَعۡنَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5704,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:33","price":"et des (belles) aux seins arrondis, d’une égale jeunesse,","arabic":"وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5705,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:34","price":"et coupes débordantes.","arabic":"وَكَأۡسٗا دِهَاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5706,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:35","price":"Ils n’y entendront ni futilités ni mensonges.","arabic":"لَّا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا كِذَّٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5707,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:36","price":"A titre de récompense de ton Seigneur et à titre de don abondant.","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَآءً حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5708,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:37","price":"du Seigneur des cieux et de la terre et de ce qui existe entre eux, le Tout Miséricordieux; ils n’osent nullement Lui adresser la parole.","arabic":"رَّبِّ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا بَيۡنَهُمَا ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِۖ لَا يَمۡلِكُونَ مِنۡهُ خِطَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5709,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:38","price":"Le jour où l’Esprit [1024] et les Anges se dresseront en rangs, nul ne saura parler, sauf celui à qui le Tout Miséricordieux aura accordé la permission, et qui dira la vérité.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلرُّوحُ وَٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ صَفّٗاۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنۡ أَذِنَ لَهُ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5710,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1024] L’Esprit: Gabriel; on a cependant attribué au mot d’autres significations.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:39","price":"Ce jour-là est inéluctable. Que celui qui veut prenne donc refuge auprès de son Seigneur.","arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلۡحَقُّۖ فَمَن شَآءَ ٱتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ مَـَٔابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5711,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"78:40","price":"Nous vous avons avertis d’un châtiment bien proche, le jour où l’homme verra ce que ses deux mains ont préparé ; et l’infidèle dira : \"Hélas pour moi ! Comme j’aurais aimé n’être que poussière.\"","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنذَرۡنَٰكُمۡ عَذَابٗا قَرِيبٗا يَوۡمَ يَنظُرُ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مَا قَدَّمَتۡ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُولُ ٱلۡكَافِرُ يَٰلَيۡتَنِي كُنتُ تُرَٰبَۢا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5712,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba","Chapter An-Naba","Naba","Surah Naba","Chapter Naba","An Naba","Surah An Naba","Chapter An Naba","Surah 78","Chapter 78","The Tidings","النبأ"]}